zou-flow commands:

    sync            synchronize changes
    sku
        enter       enter SKU
        config      [de]activate SKU submodules
        info        display SKU info
    wip
        start       create and checkout WIP
        enter       checkout WIP
        exit        exit WIP mode
        update      merge DEV | PROD into WIP
        release     merge WIP into WIP | DEV | PROD
        finish      release, exit and delete WIP
        share       push active WIP
    dev
        enter       checkout DEV branches
        attach      attach to DEV branches
        release     merge DEV branches into PROD branches (VNEXTs)
        vupdate     update version resources on DEV branch
    prod
        enter       checkout VNEXT or VLAST
        release     release VNEXT (recursive)
